ead, Ruth (14 July 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2173507/London-Olympics-2012-Cambodian-garment-workers-paid-just-10-week-make-branded-2012-Games-fanwear.html\">\"Olympic shame: Meet the Cambodian garment workers paid just \u00a310 a week to make adidas' 2012 Games 'fanwear<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Daily_Mail\" title=\"Daily Mail\">Daily Mail</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">9 September</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Daily+Mail&amp;rft.atitle=Olympic+shame%3A+Meet+the+Cambodian+garment+workers+paid+just+%C2%A310+a+week+to+make+adidas%27+2012+Games+%27fanwear%E2%80%99&amp;rft.date=2012-07-14&amp;rft.aulast=Whitehead&amp;rft.aufirst=Ruth&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-2173507%2FLondon-Olympics-2012-Cambodian-garment-workers-paid-just-10-week-make-branded-2012-Games-fanwear.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALabour+Behind+the+Label\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a href=\"/wiki/Lucy_Siegle\" title=\"Lucy Siegle\">Siegle, Lucy</a> (7 April 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2012/apr/07/hennes-mauritz-h-and-m\">\"Is H&amp;M the new home of ethical fashion?\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Observer\" title=\"The Observer\">The Observer</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Observer&amp;rft.atitle=Is+H%26M+the+new+home+of+ethical+fashion%3F&amp;rft.date=2012-04-07&amp;rft.aulast=Siegle&amp;rft.aufirst=Lucy&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2F2012%2Fapr%2F07%2Fhennes-mauritz-h-and-m&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALabour+Behind+the+Label\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-ft-taylor-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-ft-taylor_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-ft-taylor_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Taylor, Andrew (11 June 2007). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/54d8a76a-17b7-11dc-86d1-000b5df10621.html\">\"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">'</span>Sweatshop' alert for Olympics\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Financial_Times\" title=\"Financial Times\">Financial Times</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">9 September</span> 2014</span>. <q>Research by the Playfair Alliance \u2013 supported by the Trades Union Congress and the British-based Labour Behind the Label [...] Maggie Burns, who chairs Labour Behind the Label \u2013 the British arm of the international Clean Clothes campaign,</q></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Financial+Times&amp;rft.atitle=%27Sweatshop%27+alert+for+Olympics&amp;rft.date=2007-06-11&amp;rft.aulast=Taylor&amp;rft.aufirst=Andrew&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcms%2Fs%2F0%2F54d8a76a-17b7-11dc-86d1-000b5df10621.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALabour+Behind+the+Label\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-independent-mcpherson-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-independent-mcpherson_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">McPherson, Poppy (16 September 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/news/cambodian-textile-workers-who-supply-uk-clothing-stores-starving-and-suffering-mass-faintings-8820468.html\">\"Cambodian textile workers who supply UK clothing stores 'starving' and suffering 'mass faintings<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Independent\" title=\"The Independent\">The Independent</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Independent&amp;rft.atitle=Cambodian+textile+workers+who+supply+UK+clothing+stores+%27starving%27+and+suffering+%27mass+faintings%27&amp;rft.date=2013-09-16&amp;rft.aulast=McPherson&amp;rft.aufirst=Poppy&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Ffashion%2Fnews%2Fcambodian-textile-workers-who-supply-uk-clothing-stores-starving-and-suffering-mass-faintings-8820468.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALabour+Behind+the+Label\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/the-real-cost-of-fashion-a-special-report-400611.html\">\"The real cost of fashion: a special report\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Independent\" title=\"The Independent\">The Independent</a></i>. 16 November 2007<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=a